# NOTE: web/ (the built React bundle) and assets/icon.* ARE committed on
# purpose so this wrapper is a self-contained, CI-buildable unit — the
# GitHub Actions workflow can produce the Windows .exe / macOS .app without
# needing Node or the (private) frontend source. Refresh web/ + the icons
# locally with ./build.sh (macOS/Linux) or build.bat (Windows) whenever the
# frontend changes, then commit the result.
